rs can exploit.</p></div><div class=3D"card term" data-search=3D"vulnerabil=
ity assessment  identifying and documenting vulnerabilities within systems =
or networks. ">
    <div class=3D"top"><span class=3D"term">Vulnerability assessment</span>=
</div>
    <p class=3D"def">Identifying and documenting vulnerabilities within sys=
tems or networks.</p></div><div class=3D"card term" data-search=3D"wireless=
 security  techniques and technologies for securing wireless networks such =
