orks such as Wi-Fi and Bluetooth.</p></div><div class=3D"card term" data-se=
arch=3D"worm  malware that self-replicates and spreads across networks with=
out user intervention, potentially causing congestion or damage. ">
    <div class=3D"top"><span class=3D"term">Worm</span></div>
    <p class=3D"def">Malware that self-replicates and spreads across networ=
ks without user intervention, potentially causing congestion or damage.</p>=
</div><div class=3D"card term" data-search=3D"zero-day  a software vulnerab=
ility unknown to the vendor and therefore potentially exploitable before a =
