    <div class=3D"top"><span class=3D"term">Zero-day</span></div>
    <p class=3D"def">A software vulnerability unknown to the vendor and the=
refore potentially exploitable before a fix exists.</p></div><div class=3D"=
card term" data-search=3D"zero-day exploit  an attack that takes advantage =
of a vulnerability not yet known to the software vendor or security communi=
ty. ">
    <div class=3D"top"><span class=3D"term">Zero-day exploit</span></div>
    <p class=3D"def">An attack that takes advantage of a vulnerability not =
yet known to the software vendor or security community.</p></div><div class=
=3D"card term" data-search=3D"zone  a logical network division in microsoft=
 ad for managing network resources and security. ">
    <div class=3D"top"><span class=3D"term">Zone</span></div>
    <p class=3D"def">A logical network division in Microsoft AD for managin=
g network resources and security.</p></div><div class=3D"card term" data-se=
arch=3D"zoning  dividing a san into logical groups to control access and im=
